  "detailed_description": "<h1>HELP US WITH THE DEVELOPMENT</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Follow us on:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/945461d378be009c5850c70ab55d537c.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/f9c1e888cac90423baccda186e049d66.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=206 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/a395e0db1bfffe8475eadf0c8f3353ac.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=206 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/b60c0cc7d11cf584bbd02b6758aec628.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=206 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/eb01f6e19188dce270f66d11ecfc5c5a.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wondered what it's like to be a villager?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>My Village Life</strong> gives this feeling into your hands. Quests from other dwellers with different rewards. Grow your own crops in your garden, chop wood then sell it for great money. The game has several obtainable vehicles for different purposes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/88106d811e5be1e0d4a324a81d8db033.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tavern is open 7/24, giving you enough time to get drunk and won't be able to go home. If alcohol didn't catch you, there are other activities, like hunting, fishing, forest jobs, farming jobs, run businesses, helping people or discovering the secrets that the village holds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ffb1158242da5682f06e98b6217b76d0.poster.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ffb1158242da5682f06e98b6217b76d0.webm?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ffb1158242da5682f06e98b6217b76d0.mp4?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/c1d9f12c48fe991b7947df37bc4b2317.poster.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/c1d9f12c48fe991b7947df37bc4b2317.webm?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/c1d9f12c48fe991b7947df37bc4b2317.mp4?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open world gameplay</strong>, much to explore,large map with various weather and exciting cave system and with various weather<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/523ff830855e7257f557251ae771831a.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Living nature</strong> with pigs, deers, rabbits, birds, bears and other animals <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/e98d02ab03f8656d8b8d97bd805b6888.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/97e64a6fb36f0f94b421290eab01dc8c.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many cars, motorbikes, bus, trucks, tractors, airplane, trailers</strong>, agricultural tools and other are available to drive and use<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/e6702661fef8d7ef0ee7958b45f75b62.avif?t=1768472547\" width=200 height=112 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/3d15b92807f1be1c000a7bd12d224b01.avif?t=1768472547\" width=200 height=112 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/cf463a29dbf55e87a0684f1fa4771e3f.avif?t=1768472547\" width=200 height=112 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/830c7622e3d91cefdad736d012f0627a.avif?t=1768472547\" width=200 height=112 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/eb45e5afc7caaeec6b033c2539fc5a0a.avif?t=1768472547\" width=200 height=112 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ce3695bcbfc596d81c41f451cd05a547.avif?t=1768472547\" width=200 height=112 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizing vehicles</strong> with permormance, cosmetic and painting options<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/faa4e96968809b97bd4fda2de7df99ba.poster.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/faa4e96968809b97bd4fda2de7df99ba.webm?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/faa4e96968809b97bd4fda2de7df99ba.mp4?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several and varied <strong>quests and missions</strong> to help your villager friends and get some money<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/441121ec288d480e7f150532cc2b7c9d.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the secrets</strong> of your family and get to the end of the main story<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ef016bad836f8c73594f7592e822b09a.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Become a rally racer</strong> and get yourself into the mud to win Top Beer's TSD rallies <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/f2b01d90aad8d033571657171c8a1fab.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Run businesses</strong> to outgrow your village and be a millionaire<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/e6e14646bcdeb3715a8e4aea058a03e8.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/1ee480c318733087cc9508b200f15c56.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ce373894cbdaf40d8665eb9b8dd51044.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cruise around on the map in <strong>winter season</strong> and do Christmas jobs<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/34e219e5fb6dfd5ddba3bf7a3ed2c7b8.poster.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=364 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/34e219e5fb6dfd5ddba3bf7a3ed2c7b8.webm?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/34e219e5fb6dfd5ddba3bf7a3ed2c7b8.mp4?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find all <strong>hidden vehicle parts</strong> and finish that someone had started</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/2dcd324de451a59417fbc203c2950691.avif?t=1768472547\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras_big/2dcd324de451a59417fbc203c2950691.avif?t=1768472547 width=800 height=160 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Co-op mode is evolve the gameplay to higher experience. Now our lonely villager can make his job with his (alkoholic) friends. This mode open much opportunity to have fun in the game and it will increasing by all added missions in the future. You can make 2, 4 or 6 max players rooms for your friends and you can pick of public or private rooms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's jump in it together and find all secrets of this seems peaceful village!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/c571f76b7e49828fd591810287b920d5.avif?t=1768472547\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras_big/c571f76b7e49828fd591810287b920d5.avif?t=1768472547 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wondered what it's like to be a villager?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>My Village Life</strong> gives this feeling into your hands. Quests from other dwellers with different rewards. Grow your own crops in your garden, chop wood then sell it for great money. The game has several obtainable vehicles for different purposes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/88106d811e5be1e0d4a324a81d8db033.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tavern is open 7/24, giving you enough time to get drunk and won't be able to go home. If alcohol didn't catch you, there are other activities, like hunting, fishing, forest jobs, farming jobs, run businesses, helping people or discovering the secrets that the village holds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ffb1158242da5682f06e98b6217b76d0.poster.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ffb1158242da5682f06e98b6217b76d0.webm?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/ffb1158242da5682f06e98b6217b76d0.mp4?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/c1d9f12c48fe991b7947df37bc4b2317.poster.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/c1d9f12c48fe991b7947df37bc4b2317.webm?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/c1d9f12c48fe991b7947df37bc4b2317.mp4?t=1768472547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open world gameplay</strong>, much to explore,large map with various weather and exciting cave system and with various weather<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/523ff830855e7257f557251ae771831a.avif?t=1768472547\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Living nature</strong> with pigs, deers, rabbits, birds, bears and other animals <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/e98d02ab03f8656d8b8d97bd805b6888.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/97e64a6fb36f0f94b421290eab01dc8c.avif?t=1768472547\" width=300 height=168 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many cars, motorbikes, bus, trucks, tractors, airplane, trailers</strong>, agricultural tools and other are available to drive and use<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/e6702661fef8d7ef0ee7958b45f75b62.avif?t=1768472547\" width=200 height=112 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1385780/extras/3d15b92807f1be1c000a7bd12d224b01.avif?t=1768472547\" width=200 height=112 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_c